{"article_id":"u0kK7ItssySrln3s","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate candidate Beto O ' Rourke greets supporters at the \" Turn out for Texas Rally with Willie & Beto \" event in Austin , Texas , September 29 , 2018 .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"( Erich Schlegel/Reuters )","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"It ' s enough","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"to drive even the most mild-mannered Texan crazy .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Attention , journalists of America :","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Time is running out !","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"You have under three weeks left","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to publish your last batch of over-the-top pre-election puff pieces on Texas Democrat/cross-country liberal sensation/wing-and-a-prayer Senate candidate Beto O ' Rourke !","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"It is here that we must face the difficult truth :","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Barring a GOP-related disaster of some sort ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"O ' Rourke","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"- he of that ineffable \" cool factor \" and \" special sauce , \"","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"at least according to easily impressed columnists at the Washington Post -","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"is likely to lose big .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"According to the latest polls ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Senator Ted Cruz leads him by anywhere between seven and nine points .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Tuesday ' s debate between the two , meanwhile , was so mismatched","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"that O ' Rourke ' s best moment might have involved a random deer-in-the-headlights story","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"in which he described","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"how he \" got to meet this blind squirrel","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"who is slowly regaining its sight . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"In summary , this year ' s Betomania","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"- a somewhat weird phenomenon ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"as we ' ll explore in a bit -","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"seems set to disappear from view just as quickly","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"as it arrived , at least in the Lone Star State .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"On one hand , this possibility warms my heart ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"given that in my neck of Texas , it has grown rather exasperating to have to wade through 15,000 blaring BETO yard signs","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"when I ' m simply trying to get a breakfast taco or four .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"On the other hand , I also feel a tinge of melancholy and regret about all of this ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"given that I never got my act together enough","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"to print ironic t-shirts with the following brilliant slogan","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"I made up all by myself :","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" You BETO vote for Ted Cruz . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Anyway , back to the matter at hand .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"I ' d like to further discuss the debate between O ' Rourke and Ted Cruz , and also actual policy issues , and also perhaps the fact","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that many people in politics seem to be slowly going insane .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"But first , can we talk about how embarrassing Betomania is ?","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Friends , I am deeply concerned for our culture .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"When you look at a middle-aged establishment politician as an icon of \" rock star \" cool ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"you ' re doing something wrong .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" Skateboarding Beto O ' Rourke Shreds Whataburger Parking Lot , \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"read an actual recent headline on the website of the Dallas Morning News .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"This all sounds really rad and sick and gnarly and whatever","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"until you actually watch the video ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"which features O ' Rourke gently coasting around the parking lot , soccer-dad style ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"looking precariously close to biting the dust","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"when he gives a bystander a high five .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Don ' t get mad :","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"I ' m not judging !","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"I would do exactly the same thing ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"except I ' d probably actually fall !","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"But no wide-eyed journalist would write a headline","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that I \" shredded \" anything ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"nor credulously act","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"like I belonged on the cover of Thrasher magazine .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Of the countless head-scratching elements of the O ' Rourke phenomenon , one wins handily as the head-scratchingest of all :","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"A troubling percentage of the Betomaniacs","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"I have met in Texas","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"moved here","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"after fleeing places","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"ruined by Beto ' s favored policies .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"These locales are often expensive ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"increasingly dysfunctional ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"wildly overregulated ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"sometimes mystifyingly poop-ridden","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"despite being wildly overregulated","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"( here ' s looking at you , San Francisco ! ) ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"and inevitably run by Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Why does no one seem to make this connection ?","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"I don ' t know !","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"One hero in Austin has taken to posting stickers around town","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"featuring an image of a giant locust ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"paired with the following text :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" I MIGRATED TO A THRIVING TEXAS FROM A LEFTIST","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"[ NIGHTMARE ]","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"AND NOW I ' M VOTING FOR BETO FOR SENATE. \"","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"( The posters feature a word much worse than \" nightmare , \"","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"which I ' m not reprinting","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"because I run a PG-13 column here . )","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"\" But Heather , \" you might be thinking .","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"\" Surely you must have seen the countless articles in national publications","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"describing","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"how annoying Ted Cruz is","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"and how Beto O ' Rourke is going to lead our generation","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"in rising up above the terrible cynicism","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that dominates modern politics ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"acting as a bridge","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"uniting and respecting the diverse voices of Texans","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"as long as you join in lockstep support for things like abortion on demand , higher taxes , and a list of leftist hobbyhorses","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that drive out-of-state donors wild ! \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Why yes , thanks , I have read those articles .","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"I laugh every time !","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"I used to think","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"that O ' Rourke didn ' t even really want to win","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"- if he did , after all ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"wouldn ' t he at least pretend to be even a teensy bit more moderate ? -","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"but Tuesday ' s debate disabused me of that notion .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Judging by the slightly panicked facial expression","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that emerged from time to time ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"he really does want to win .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"( As an aside , I don ' t know","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"which jokester at the TV station made O ' Rourke stand in front of an image of multiple oil rigs","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"relentlessly pumping","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"while Cruz pummeled him","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"for supporting a massive gas tax ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"but sir or madam , here ' s to you . )","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"Alas ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"now that times have gotten tough , after months of nice-guy \" rise above the fray \" narratives , Mean Beto has finally emerged .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"On Tuesday , he whipped out Trump ' s old \" Lyin ' Ted \" nickname for Cruz ,","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and his campaign has launched a series of attack ads","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Cruz is engaged in \" selling paranoia and fear. \"","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Well , politics is politics .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Meanwhile , thanks to the enduring power of Betomania , even a loss this fall might be a win for O ' Rourke .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" Beto O ' Rourke Matters","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Even If He Loses , \"","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"a headline at Bloomberg recently declared .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"O ' Rourke \" defies gravity , \"","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"argued The Ringer .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Comparisons to Barack Obama flow freely ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"and the presidential speculation grows .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"\" Will Beto O ' Rourke Become President ? \"","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"asked a column at Texas Monthly back in August .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"\" It might help","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"if he loses to Ted Cruz . \"","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"Stay tuned , America .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"We live in interesting times .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"Anything can happen !","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"And Betomaniacs ,","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"if O ' Rourke does indeed lose ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"don ' t fret :","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"He ' ll undoubtedly be back","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"and BETO than ever !","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Okay , okay , I ' ll stop .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"I ' m sorry .","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"I blame the unending sea of yard signs .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"They could probably crack the best of us .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":277,"left":172,"right":276,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":142,"right":171,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":140,"right":141,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":158,"right":170,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":153,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":145,"right":152,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":143,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":8,"right":151,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":149,"right":150,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":9,"right":148,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":10,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":16,"right":156,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":17,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,